#Components list:

Electronics:
- 7 esp32 microprocessors
- 7DS18B20 Temperature Sensor mounted on a water-proof mount and 1.5 m cable
- 7 SHT31 Temperature & Humidity Sensor
- 7 breadboards
- 4.7k Ohm resistors
- Jumper wires

Hardware:
- Electric wires
- Electric power supply (5V)
- ventilated electric boxes to shade sensors 
